  <div class="comment">
    <h3 class="title"><a href="/battlestar/daybreak-part-one#comment-8819" class="active">Bullsh--</a></h3>    <div class="submitted">Submitted by Alvin (not verified) on Tue, 2009-03-17 18:34.</div>
