<p>I've noted this to folks who complain of retconning on numerous occasions, but no one seems to care.  It's something that does need to be accepted, however.  No one is going to plan out a 4-5 year show and stick to their original plan 100%.  Things change and evolve.  Better ideas emerge, lesser ones are discarded or written out.</p>
